{
  "stem": "25809.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Apparently, my father had talked to somebody from the, the Jewish advisory board and said, please do something.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Let my son escape or get him out of here.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And so I was guided, in bright daylight-- it must have been about 4 o'clock in the afternoon, I think, by then.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "In bright daylight, I just quietly walked away from the creche area in the Schouwburg.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But I was wearing my star.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And so I had a sweater that I had put over my shoulder to cover the star because I figured, by now it is important that nobody realizes that I am Jewish or that anybody sees me wearing a Jewish star because I may get picked up again.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I am trying desperately to pluck that star off my, off my chest because it was sewn on.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And unfortunately, my mother had done a hell of a job.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I had a rough time trying to get that, that star.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I keep on plucking away, plucking away under my sweater, trying to literally tear that star off my chest.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Meanwhile, I'm walking.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I'm walking away quietly because I figured I have to put on act that I'm not in a hurry.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "If I run, I'm going to draw attention to myself.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So I'm just walking away quietly, and I started walking and walking.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Finally, I get to a, to a bridge.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I figure, I've got to get rid of this star.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And finally, I got that star-- finally-- off my, off my, off my, my clothing, and I kind of rubbed it in a little ball and rubbing it and rubbing it.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
